For nvidia graphic card users:

i have found the solution of the problem :
nothing happens after clicking launcher.

the problen is with physx.
just copy the file 'nvcplui.exe' from c:\Program Files\NVIDIA Corporation\Control Panel Client and paste it into c:\WINDOWS\system32

problem solved.
run launcher play and enjoy the game.
